          <br/><br/>Add a second HTTP module branching from the same webhook trigger. POST to Google&rsquo;s Enhanced Conversions endpoint with your Conversion ID, hashed email address, hashed phone number (where available), and order value. Google uses SHA-256 hashed customer data to match server events to Google account identities &mdash; this is what recovers iOS-lost conversions in Google Ads.
