    <p><strong>EMQ scores range from 0&ndash;10.</strong> Higher scores improve how accurately TikTok can match server events to real users &mdash; directly improving ad attribution and algorithm quality. Scores of 6&ndash;8 are typical for Shopify stores sending all four signals below.</p>
